headline: What's driving confidence in Big Banks ahead of earnings
summary: Big Bank stocks, including JPMorgan (JPM) and Morgan Stanley (MS), were recently upgraded by KBW just before bank earnings kick off next week. KBW managing director and head of US bank research Christopher McGratty and Yahoo Finance Senior Reporter David Hollerith join Market Domination Overtime to break down what's driving sentiment across the banking sector. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination Overtime here.

headline: Bank of America, N.A. Announces Redemptions of $2,000,000,000 5.650% Senior Bank Notes and $400,000,000 Floating Rate Senior Bank Notes, Due August 2025
summary: Bank of America, N.A. announced today that it will redeem on July 18, 2025 all $2,000,000,000 principal amount outstanding of its 5.650% Senior Bank Notes, due August 2025 (CUSIP No. 06428CAC8) (the "Fixed Rate Notes"), and all $400,000,000 principal amount of its Floating Rate Senior Bank Notes, due August 2025 (CUSIP No. 06428CAD6) (the "Floating Rate Notes" and, together with the Fixed Rate Notes, the "Notes").
